title: Sleepy Hollow (1999) [NDS.movieS] .dpg.SCOPE
description:
nDs-mPeG, usually abbreviated DPG, is a special format of MPEG-1 video specifically for playback using the homebrew Moonshell program for the Nintendo DS. The video is encoded on a computer and then transferred, along with Moonshell, to the DS for playback.






Director:Tim Burton

Writers:Washington Irving & Kevin Yagher

Release Date:7 January 2000 (UK)

Genre:Horror | Mystery

Tagline:Who will it come for next?!

Plot:Ichabod Crane is sent to Sleepy Hollow to investigate the decapitations of 3 people with the culprit being the legendary apparition, the Headless Horseman
